metadata.name: Divine Watcher
metadata.description:
In realms above, where hope takes flight,
The Divine Watcher, with wings of light,
A guardian of dreams, a celestial guide,
Navigates the heavens, by our side.

With wings unfurled, it soars with grace,
Bringing hope to every earthly place.
Through trials and storms, it carries our dreams,
On radiant wings, with purpose it gleams.

3584 x 5376 px
